      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Set the mast vertical.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Lower the carriage completely.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>On full free lift and full free triple lift models, the bottom of the inner mast must
        be flush with the bottom of the stationary mast.
            </p>
            <p>
               <fig id="fig_frt_fqz_5gc">
                  <image href="media/image860.png" id="image_irt_fqz_5gc" placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Measure the distance from the bottom of the inner upright to
the bottom of carriage bearing.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>The measurement (A) must be as follows in Chart below.</p>
